<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="walk-n">walk <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɔːk/    美 /wɔːk/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>走路；散步：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>go ( out ) for a walk</strong>
出去散步</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>take / have a walk</strong>
散步</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>take</strong> Tina, the dog, <strong>for a walk</strong> every afternoon.
我每天下午都带小狗蒂娜去散步。</p><footer>北师大⑦ – 1</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>步行距离；行走路程：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The office is a <strong>ten</strong> - <strong>minute walk</strong> from here.
从这里到办公室要步行10分钟。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="a-walk-of-life">a walk of life</h3>
<p>1.<strong>行业；职业；社会阶层(background)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Our volunteers include people <strong>from all walks of life</strong>.
我们的志愿者包括各界人士。</p></div></div>